text:
Grand Central Parkway, north from about 69th Road, showing the route where the highway was later constructed. View 2 shows the course of the Parkway, seen in a different direction.

October 1, 1935
Views 1,2

P. L. Sperr
title: Queens: Grand Central Parkwa - 69th Road
